**Custom Attributes** are used to build custom forms and gather input from the user.

## Types of Custom Attributes

* [User-Defined Custom Attributes](/reference/custom-attributes/user-defined): Custom Attributes you can create on demand.

Platform OS also provides a few Custom Attributes for you to use: 

* [Custom Addresses](/reference/custom-attributes/custom-addresses): used to add one or many addresses to the configuration.

* [Custom Images](/reference/custom-attributes/custom-images): used to add one or many images to the configuration.

* [Custom Attachments](/reference/custom-attributes/custom-attachments): used to add one or many files to the configuration.
